#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Creferences%5Ckeycloak-realm.md:105
msgid ""
"`test-hr-denhaag` is the primary HR test account — it holds the `hr-"
"medewerker` realm role and can start onboarding processes and view the "
"Afgeronde onboardingen archive. `test-onboarded-denhaag` simulates an "
"employee who has already been onboarded; logging in with this account "
"triggers an auto-fetch of the completed onboarding record for `emp-test-01`."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Creferences%5Ckeycloak-realm.md:107
msgid ""
"`test-hr-flevoland` is the Flevoland HR account for onboarding "
"infrastructure employees. `test-infra-flevoland` is a pre-configured "
"infrastructure team member (`employeeId: EMP-FLV-001`) who can start and "
"work through the RIP Fase 1 process."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Creferences%5Ckeycloak-realm.md:111
msgid "Re-importing the realm"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Creferences%5Ckeycloak-realm.md:113
msgid "After modifying `config/keycloak/ronl-realm.json`:"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Creferences%5Ckeycloak-realm.md:115
msgid ""
"# On the VM, for ACC\n"
"docker exec keycloak-acc /opt/keycloak/bin/kc.sh import \\\n"
"  --file /opt/keycloak/data/import/ronl-realm.json \\\n"
"  --override true\n"
"\n"
"# Restart to apply\n"
"cd ~/keycloak/acc\n"
"docker compose restart keycloak-acc\n"
"\n"
"# On the VM, for PROD\n"
"docker exec keycloak-prod /opt/keycloak/bin/kc.sh import \\\n"
"  --file /opt/keycloak/data/import/ronl-realm.json \\\n"
"  --override true\n"
"\n"
"cd ~/keycloak/prod\n"
"docker compose restart keycloak-prod"
msgstr ""
